        <text>Once per turn when you make an attack roll, ability check, or saving throw, you can choose to trigger an Arcane Anomaly (see page 233). If you do, you make that roll with advantage. You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum once). You regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.

Source:	Sebastian Crowe's Guide to Drakkenheim (Third Party)</text>
