You choose the damage type from either fire, cold, lightning, acid, or poison. The arrows or bolts deal an additional 1d4 damage of the chosen type. Any previously imbued arrows or bolts lose this magic if you use this feature again.

At 12th level, the additional damage increases to 1d6.



Source:	Sebastian Crowe's Guide to Drakkenheim (Third Party)</text>
