In a new form, the dragon retains their alignment, hit points, Hit Dice, ability to speak, proficiencies, Legendary Resistance, lair actions, and Intelligence, Wisdom, and Charisma scores, as well as this action. Their statistics and capabilities are otherwise replaced by those of the new form, except any class features or legendary actions of that form.</text>
