      </feature>
      <feature optional="YES">
        <name>Cycle of Contamination (Circle of Contamination)</name>
        <text>Though your magic is infused with contaminated power, you have also learned ways to effectively expel these energies. You can cast the purge contamination* spell as an action without expending a spell slot. You don't need to provide the material components when you cast the spell in this way, and the target does not gain any exhaustion levels from this casting of the spell. When you cast purge contamination* in this way, you can't do so again until you finish a long rest.






Source:	Sebastian Crowe's Guide to Drakkenheim (Third Party)</text>
