        <name>Draw Corruption (Circle of Contamination)</name>
        <text>You gain the ability to draw contamination into yourself to empower your magic. Once per turn as a bonus action, you can gain one Contamination Level. If you do, you regain one use of your Wild Shape feature.






Source:	Sebastian Crowe's Guide to Drakkenheim (Third Party)</text>
