      <feature optional="YES">
        <name>Defile Elements (Circle of Contamination)</name>
        <text>You learn the summon delerium elemental spell, and always have this spell prepared (it doesn't count against the number of druid spells you can prepare). You can cast it once without a spell slot, material
component, or gaining a contamination level, and you regain the ability to do so when you finish a long rest. When you cast the spell, you can modify it so that it doesn't require concentration. When you do, the spell's duration for that casting changes to 1 minute.






Source:	Sebastian Crowe's Guide to Drakkenheim (Third Party)</text>
